<h2><strong>What is Functional Fragrance?</strong></h2>
<p>The term "functional fragrance" refers to a category of scents designed to do more than just smell good. These fragrances are formulated with specific functions in mind, such as enhancing mood, reducing stress, boosting energy levels, and even caring for your skin or hair. The idea is to harness the power of aromatherapy—the use of natural plant extracts to promote health and well-being—within the realm of fine fragrance.</p>
<p>Functional fragrances are developed using scientific principles that explore the connection between scent and emotion. By combining olfactory expertise with insights from psychology and neurobiology, these fragrances aim to create meaningful and positive impacts on the wearer's mental and emotional state.</p>
